                li( role="presentation")
                    a( href="#services" aria-controls="services" role="tab" data-toggle="tab")
                        |Explore All Services

            .tab-content.panel-body.bordered-tab-body
                .tab-pane.fade.in.active(role="tabpanel" id="home")
                    p Since 2003, TriCounties Speech Services, Inc. has been a leader in early-intervention services and speech
                        | therapy for the South Santa Clara, San Benito, and Monterey Counties.

                    p Our therapy services include:

                    ul(style="list-style: disc; margin-left: 25px")
                        li Early Intervention Services Therapy for children 3 and under at risk for developmental delays,
                            | including home-based sessions, intended to help them reach their unique developmental milestones.
                        li Speech-Language Therapy Helping your child learn to use & understand language, using a wide range of
                            | tools and interventions (toys, play-like therapy, formal testing, speech curricula, etc.).
                .tab-pane.fade( role="tabpanel" id="services")
                    .row
                        .col-md-3
                            ul.nav.nav-pills.nav-stacked
                                li.active
                                    a( href="#articulation" aria-controls="home" role="tab" data-toggle="tab")
                                        | Articulation
                                li( role="presentation")
                                    a( href="#motor" aria-controls="motor" role="tab" data-toggle="tab")
                                        | Explore Services
                                li( role="presentation")
                                    a( href="#language" aria-controls="language" role="tab" data-toggle="tab")
                                        | Language
                                li( role="presentation")
                                    a( href="#care" aria-controls="care" role="tab" data-toggle="tab")
                                        | Self Care
                                li( role="presentation")
                                    a( href="#sensory" aria-controls="sensory" role="tab" data-toggle="tab")
                                        | Sensory
                                li( role="presentation")
                                    a( href="#social" aria-controls="social" role="tab" data-toggle="tab")
                                        | Social Skills
                        .col-md-9
                            .tab-content
                                .tab-pane.fade.in.active(role="tabpanel" id="articulation")
                                    p
                                        |Articulation: The movement of the tongue, lips, jaw, and other speech organs
                                        |in order to make speech sounds.
                                    include ../services/articulation
                                .tab-pane.fade.in(role="tabpanel" id="motor")
                                    p
                                        |Fine & Gross Motor: The ability to use large and small muscle groups that
                                        |coordinate body movements involved in activities such as walking, running,
                                        |jumping, throwing, writing, maintaining balance, buttoning, cutting, visual
                                        |tracking, and tracing.
                                    include ../services/motor
                                .tab-pane.fade.in(role="tabpanel" id="language")
                                    p
                                        |Language Development: The process by which children come to understand and
                                        |communicate language during early childhood.
                                    include ../services/language
                                .tab-pane.fade.in(role="tabpanel" id="care")
                                    p
                                        |Intentional actions you take to care for your physical, mental and emotional health.
                                    include ../services/care
                                .tab-pane.fade.in(role="tabpanel" id="sensory")
                                    p
                                        | Sensory Development: The maturing of the five familiar senses: hearing,
                                        | smell, taste, touch, and vision. It involves the way your childâ€™s nervous
                                        | system receives input from these senses and then forms an appropriate motor
                                        | or behavioral response, also known as sensory processing.
                                    include ../services/sensory
                                .tab-pane.fade.in(role="tabpanel" id="social")
                                    p
                                        | Social Skills: The skills we use to communicate and interact with each other,
                                        | both verbally and non-verbally, through gestures, body language and our personal appearance.
                                    include ../services/social
